Definition: an elaborate or deceitful scheme contrived to deceive or evade
Example: his testimony was just a contrivance to throw us off the track
Synonyms: stratagem, dodge, adj, all, artful, dodgy, scheme, an, elaborate, or, deceitful, contrived, to, deceive, evade, his, testimony, was, just, a, throw, us, off, the, track
Category: noun.cognition
